<P>
   LATIN-GRAMMY-AWARDS (Undated) _ When the first Latin Grammy
Awards are broadcast Wednesday night, the show will mark the first
time a major U.S. television network has agreed to devote two
prime-time hours to multilingual programming _ the talk will be
mostly in English and Spanish, the singing in Spanish and
Portuguese. By Mireya Navarro. &QL;
