track of everybody's birthday, this is a gentle reminder: It's time
to think about scheduling your annual furnace inspection and
cleaning. To those who can't remember their last oil change,
physical or their own birthdays, maybe this should be the year you
finally do something about the black smoke billowing from your
registers. (Cummings, Dayton Daily News). 24.
