   GARDENING-LIFE _ A gardening column by Lee May. This week: It's
tough for garden writers to admit they can't grow something. But
when it comes to angel trumpet, Lee May throws up his hands. That
is, he did until he met Midtown Atlanta gardener J.J. Jones. (May,
Atlanta Journal-Constitution)
