</P>
<P>
   MEN'S-MAGAZINES (San Francisco) _ In the photo she's wearing a
tight two-piece. Legs parted, head thrown back, eyes closed, she
smiles. The woman is not a Playmate of the Month but Olympic high
jumper Amy Acuff in Esquire magazine's cover story/pictorial
