recent issues of men's magazines reveals the latest sex symbol is
the female athlete. By MARGOT MAGOWAN.
</P>
<P>
   WONG-COLUMN (San Francisco) _ After a soccer or hockey game, I'd
drive my son Sam to a tiny building in the North Oakland, where
Harry Yaglijian dispensed his Original Kasper's hotdog. Most of the
time Sam and I stood in line, awaiting Harry's attention. The wait
was worth it, both for the scrumptious hot dogs and for Harry's
warm greetings. He died last year, and legions of his customers
still remember his infectious friendliness. By WILLIAM WONG.
</P>
