time for embezzling money from a pension fund in the 1970s, goes to
the Texas lottery headquarters to collect the more than $20 million
he won from the state lottery. By JOHN GONZALEZ.
</P>
<P>
   SPACE-STATION (Houston) _ Astronauts from the shuttle Atlantis
plug four fresh batteries into the international space station, a
job that required a hammer, a chisel and a bit of force. By MARK
CARREAU.
