   CANADA-SHOOTING (Quebec) _ Investigative reporter known for
coverage of motorcycle gangs is shot and killed. The attack comes
hours after Quebec urges the federal government to suspend civil
liberties of bikers by outlawing membership in the Hells Angels,
Rock Machine and other outlaw groups. By Colin Nickerson. 1000
words.
</P>
<P>
   IRELAND-CLINTON (Washington) _ Protestant First Minister David
Trimble meets with President Clinton at the White House. Clinton
might announce he will make a final trip to Ireland before he
leaves office. By Susan Milligan. 800 words.
