political cast _ Joseph Lieberman, Lynne Cheney, and John McCain _
give dramatic performances, blaming the entertainment industry for
polluting the popular culture and making it nearly impossible for
parents to police the films, recordings, and video games that amuse
their children. By Mary Leonard. 800 words. &UR;  &LR; (w and e coding)
