   NATIONAL
</P>
<P>
   HILLARY-DEBATE _ BUFFALO, N.Y. _ Coverage of the first Hillary
Clinton/Rick Lazio debate from Buffalo, with Tim Russert
moderating. (Vejnoska, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 25.
</P>
<P>
   DROUGHT _ Water managers are seriously concerned over the lack
of rain now. They're declaring a LOW water emergency for Lake
Okeechobee, issuing a shortage warning for the cities around the
lake, and asking for ``voluntary'' cutbacks in Palm Beach, Broward
and Dade. Among the ideas they're seriously considering are pumping
incredibly polluted water back into Lake Okeechobee _ or, if that
doesn't fly, pumping Lake O dry in order to keep meeting the
farmers' needs. (King, Palm Beach Post).
</P>
