   COKE-NEWMACHINES _ ATLANTA _ Coca-Cola Co. is rolling out new
vending machines that dispense all of its products, from cans of
Coke to bottles of orange juice and water. The glass-front machines
use a mechanical bar to fetch drinks and set them gently in a
receptacle. Coke hopes the Maytag-made machines will boost
