<P>
   COXNET LIFESTYLES 0916: POP'S PRINCESSES: The newest teen pop
sensations _ Britney Spears, Christina Aguilera, Jessica Simpson
and Mandy Moore _ are turning some heads, and not just for their
musical abilities. Their suggestive song lyrics, sultry dance moves
and skimpy clothing have turned these ex-Mousketeers and former
church choir members into teen-age sex symbols. That has some
people worried about whether kids are plunging too early into an
adult lifestyle. (Allmon, Waco Herald-Tribune) Art includes a
4-column color photo of Britney Spears in concert.
</P>
<P>
   WITH: PRIMER ON THE STARS -- A list of facts about Britney
Spears, Christina Aguilera, Jessica Simpson and Mandy Moore.
