<HEADLINE>
`N SYNC-ERATOR
</HEADLINE>
  (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
 
 
By SANDRA BARRERA 
c.2000 Los Angeles Daily News 
<TEXT>
<P>
   cc,78p3
</P>
<P>
   `N Sync is already the biggest boy group on the planet and they
just keeping getting bigger.
</P>
<P>
   On Wednesday, its members Lance Bass, JC Chasez, Joey Fatone,
Chris Kirkpatrick and Justin Timberlake unveiled a Spanish version
of the new single ``This I Promise'' on the Latin Grammy Awards.
The week before, the group took home several MTV Video Music
awards.
</P>
