 &UR; WINDOWSME _ &LR;   &LR; It's difficult to resist the temptation to poke fun
at Microsoft's claim that Windows Millennium Edition, the new
version that goes on sale today, is ``a simpler, more robust and
more useful operating system'' for home users.
</P>
