   You could, for example, point to plenty of ``enhancements'' that
hardly seem worth the price of admission ($59.95 if you upgrade
from Windows 98 by Jan. 15, 2001, around $90 thereafter, or if you
are starting from an earlier version of Windows).  &UR; BY &LR; 
